data.description:
Get away from the city and enjoy peace and serenity on this 3.05 acres(mol).  You will enjoy the fruit from the many fruit trees on the property.  There are multiple garden areas ready for a green thumb, and also grape vines.  The lot is bordered in the back by a stream and is fenced on 3 sides. (The small yard fence will not stay)
This modular homes offers a nice front deck and when you enter, you will see the seller has taken immaculate care of the place.  The carpet and woodwork still look brand new!  The washer/dryer and refrigerator will stay with this home.
There is an extra gas powered heat source in case of electric outage, an in ground storm cellar, and lots of other bonus items.
Note, the owner is packing to move, so photos are reflective of that.
The property includes 3 outside storage areas.  You won't want to miss the chance to see this!
